name: complex_lattice_clamp_idempotent_when_ordered
section: lattice-clamp
args: x:Int lo:Int hi:Int
type: Bool
expect: True
description: A clamped value should be idempotent under the same clamp when bounds are ordered.
law: (if (fuzz-lte? {lo} {hi}) (= (fuzz-min (fuzz-max (fuzz-min (fuzz-max {x} {lo}) {hi}) {lo}) {hi}) (fuzz-min (fuzz-max {x} {lo}) {hi})) True)
